"{    \"translations\": [        {            \"english_version\": \"Cuba's current president says the charges against Castro, which include conspiracy to kill US nationals and destruction of aircraft, are a political move. This statement follows the US charging Cuba's former leader with murder, increasing pressure on the regime.\",            \"english_title\": \"Cuba's President on Charges\",            \"translated_version\": \"El presidente de Cuba dice que las acusaciones contra Castro, que incluyen conspirar para matar a personas de EE.UU. y destruir aviones, son un movimiento politico. Esto pasa despues de que EE.UU. acusara al ex lider de Cuba de asesinato, aumentando la presion sobre el regimen.\",            \"translated_title\": \"Presidente de Cuba sobre Acusaciones\"        },        {            \"english_version\": \"A rare Ebola species outbreak is believed to have caused 139 deaths so far, according to the latest reports.\",            \"english_title\": \"Ebola Outbreak\",            \"translated_version\": \"Un brote raro de Ebola se cree que ha causado 139 muertes hasta ahora, segun los ultimos reportes.\",            \"translated_title\": \"Brote de Ebola\"        },        {            \"english_version\": \"Nine people deported from the US have arrived in Cuba as part of Donald Trump's efforts to reduce illegal immigration.\",            \"english_title\": \"Deportees Arrive in Cuba\",            \"translated_version\": \"Nueve personas deportadas de EE.UU. han llegado a Cuba como parte de los esfuerzos de Donald Trump para reducir la inmigracion ilegal.\",            \"translated_title\": \"Deportados Llegan a Cuba\"        },        {            \"english_version\": \"A health agency reports that sexually transmitted infections have increased due to record cases and gaps in testing and prevention.\",            \"english_title\": \"Increase in Infections\",            \"translated_version\": \"Una agencia de salud reporta que las infecciones de transmision sexual han aumentado debido a casos record y fallas en pruebas y prevencion.\",            \"translated_title\": \"Aumento de Infecciones\"        },        {            \"english_version\": \"Russia and China have shown unity on the world stage, but there are clear limits to their cooperation, according to the BBC's Russia Editor.\",            \"english_title\": \"Russia and China Cooperation\",            \"translated_version\": \"Rusia y China han mostrado unidad en el escenario mundial, pero hay limites claros a su cooperacion, segun el editor de Rusia de la BBC.\",            \"translated_title\": \"Cooperacion de Rusia y China\"        }    ]}"